Package: ephys4
Type: Package
Title: Read, analyze and plot HEKA Patchmaster files
Version: 4.0.0
Date: 2022-09-29
Author: Timm Danker
Maintainer: Timm Danker <timm.danker@nmi.de>
Description: Patchmaster raw data files can be read directly and visualized using ggplot.  
 The package also allows for setting of so called 'cursors', 
 which are user defined regions of interest on which calculations are performed. 
